comments.text:
(In reply to Dietrich Ayala (:dietrich) from comment #46)
> Comment on attachment 579848
> Patch v0.1
> 
> Review of attachment 579848:
> -----------------------------------------------------------------
> 
> i don't understand. why not leave it as-is and set dependency on that root
> cause bug?
